---> Queue vs Stack (Quick Comparison)
| Stack           | Queue                       |
|  |  |
| LIFO            | FIFO                        |
| Push / Pop      | Enqueue / Dequeue           |
| One end         | Two ends                    |
| Undo, Recursion | Scheduling, Waiting systems |

